Dexy is software for document automation. http://dexy.it

Dexy's source code is available from http://github.com/ananelson/dexy

The 'master' branch contains the most recent release of Dexy (or rather it will after 0.7.0 comes out...)
The 'develop' branch contains the most recent development version of Dexy.

Dexy is tested on Python 2.6-Python 2.7.
Dexy is tested on Windows, but not all filters are windows-compatible.

Dexy's tests can be run with the command 'nosetests'
Dexy will skip tests where 3rd party software is required but not installed.

See http://dexy.it for docs.
